summary: The full Brainstash application lands, with versioned entries, full-text search, OAuth and session auth, and a CLI.
---

The full Brainstash application: **entries** with categories, tags, and
versioning; **full-text search**; OAuth + session auth; a **CLI**; and a
Bun + SvelteKit + Drizzle/LibSQL monorepo. The toolchain migrated to **tsgo**
and dependencies were upgraded to latest.
